  .intro--content.hidden.js-intro-content
    %h1 Future Instruments 2214

    %p.intro--description.hidden.js-intro-description
      We asked 12 Artists, Musicians, Designers and Futurists, to imagine what an instrument would be 200 years from now. These predictions have been interpreted and illustrated by Kim Laughton.

